sec.p:
Kinetic evaluation was performed using two models, i.e. Modified Gompertz (1) and Logistic growth (2) were selected to perform. Each of them showed the optimal fit to the experimental data, that is confirmed by root-mean-square error (RMSE) values (3) below 10. Additionally, for selected models, the high values of determination coefficient (R2) exceeding 0.99 were achieved, confirming that these models are suitable for simulating the kinetic parameters of methane production.1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
